               <p>811. The three prisoners were again indicted for <rs id="t17891028-70-off340" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17891028-70-off340" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17891028-70-off340" type="offenceSubcategory" value="other"></interp>
               stealing various other articles
            </rs>, but the prosecutor giving no evidence, the three prisoners were all found</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17891028-70-verdict341" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17891028-70-verdict341" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17891028-70-verdict341" type="verdictSubcategory" value="noEvidence"></interp>
               NOT GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
